title: Rate of Persons with Hepatitis A or B, Italy by Regione, 2006
name: Rate of Persons with Hepatitis A or B, Italy by Regione, 2006
description:
This dataset displays the rate of persons (per 100,000) that have Hepatitis A or B by Regione for various age groups throughout Italy in 2006.  The data is also broken up by sexes and both sexes.
The data comes from Istat
